        "rtf_AtTyMN": {
          "type": "rtf",
          "settings": {
            "richtext_content": "<p>The energy, effort, and mindset brought by all the competitors on the day made the 2026 Stoic Games exactly what it was meant to be, a true test of resilience and discipline.</p><p>Whether you competed, supported, or soaked it all in, we’re so grateful to everyone that showed up and gave it their all, inspiring us all to keep pushing our limits.</p><p>You can view and download images from the event here: <a href=\"https://gymking.fotoowl.ai/\" target=\"_blank\">https://gymking.fotoowl.ai/</a></p><p>Until next time, keep training, keep showing up, and keep pushing your limits!</p>"
          }
        },
