            "richtext_content": "<h1></h1><h2>Pricing</h2><h3>What's included with your ticket</h3><p>Your ticket grants:</p><ul><li><strong>Entry to </strong><em><strong>The Stoic Games</strong></em></li><li><strong>Access to the Recovery Zone</strong> with physios, compression boots, muscle guns, and vibrating foam rollers</li><li><strong>30% OFF discount code</strong> for use on Gym King clothing, including the upcoming Stoic 2.0 Collection</li><li><strong>Custom trophy</strong> for participants who achieve 1000 points</li><li><strong>Goody bag</strong> including limited edition Stoic Games finisher medal, finisher tote bag, neutonic, and other goodies.</li></ul>"
